    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Fire screens supported upon a stand and designed so that the panels may be moved or extended by means of sliding the panels on a pole (a pole screen) or in a frame (a cheval screen).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
